#

Blackened Salmon with Tropical Salsa and Citrus Herb Rice

$30
600 kcal
Difficulty: 60%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

PescatarianGluten-Free

Tags:

Main CourseDinnerSeafood

Description

A succulent blackened salmon paired with a refreshing mango avocado salsa and served alongside cilantro lime rice, offering a vibrant and zesty meal experience.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 4 fillets
  • Mango: 1, diced
  • Avocado: 1, diced
  • Red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime: 2, juiced
  • Jalapeño: 1, finely chopped
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • Paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • Garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Brown sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • Rice: 1 cup
  • Chicken broth: 2 cups
